item.description:
Dr. Jung Sun Yoog , Bulent Gunerlap, Kim Davidson and other will provide an enchanting evening of Classical, Opera, Folk and Spirituals as a benefit for the First Presbyterian Church or Waltham. Sunday, November 28 at 7 pm.

Dr. Yoon is a classically trained pianist and harpist. Bulent Guneralap is a bass-baritone Singer who has performed worldwide. Kim Davidson is a local singer songwriter performing original folk music.

The concert will be Sunday evening at First Presbyterian Church in Waltham - 34 Alder Street Waltham Ma. Tickets are only $10 at the door. Proceeds to benefit the church Sancturary Redevelopment Fund. Coffee, tea and snacks will be provided.
item.name: Ecletic Evening of Music
